      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVERS MEET (1) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (30.04) behind Unacceptable Nik at this track. Leading chance again. OKLAHOMA BALE (5) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (30.55) at this track in a Grade 5 over 525m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. PAW ZOLTIN (4) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Unacceptable Nik (30.17) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. NOAH'S BEST (2) is in the mix after placing here at this trip last time out.",
